Class MapObjectBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.mobility.sdk.map.MapObjectBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Marker

    public abstract class MapObjectBase
extends Object
    Abstract class used to display points and bitmaps dynamically on a map.
